                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/db/derby/code/trunk/java/testing/README.htm?view=co&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/db/derby/code/trunk/java/testing/README.htm?view=co&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the purpose of&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     set tstjardir=/local/testingjars&lt;/p&gt;

